Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:07.23,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,So return to the capital—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:13.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you playing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:16.37,main,SoldierA,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you! How dare you take \NPrincess Melty hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:18.12,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:21.29,main,SoldierA,0000,0000,0000,,Fellow knights! Justice is on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:23.76,main,SoldierA,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the Devil of the Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:27.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Resorting to calling me a devil now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:29.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia! Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:00.04,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,R-Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:06.25,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:06.25,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna chase them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:07.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.59,0:01:10.96,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Mel-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:34.28,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,1)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:48.81,sign_5367_37_Lullaby_at_Dawn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(486,768)}The Devil of the Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:05.46,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:09.00,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.05,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:15.27,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,The altered footage has made its way \Nto the nearby towns and villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:18.25,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Entering them would be too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.11,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:28.34,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you try to kill the second \Nprincess in front of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:32.99,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.96,flashback,SolA,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to say to the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.92,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's a rosary from the \NThree Heroes Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.30,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Heroes Church?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:50.01,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Melromarc's state religion, which worships \Nthe Sword, Spear, and Bow Heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.90,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me... I saw it at the \Nchurch in the capital, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.77,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,The three heroes other than the Shield, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:05:01.15,flashback,SolA,0000,0000,0000,,You'll learn just how grave the sin of \Ndisturbing our country's order is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.94,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:08.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno, but it's probably another \None of the king's schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:12.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to her stupid dad, \Nwe're stuck here with nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.29,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,My father can't be behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:18.79,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could've ordered it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:22.25,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,My sister, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:27.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So she's trying to kill you and \Ntake your place as crown princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:33.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But the knights who attacked you are \Nunder the king's direct control, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.57,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be natural to assume he's in on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:44.81,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,they want to frame "The Devil of the Shield"\N for this whole plot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:47.40,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Father would never!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:49.36,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.82,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Because Father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:57.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why stick up for a scumbag like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.46,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.67,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.54,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:06.17,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't either of you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:10.71,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be \Nfighting among yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:14.35,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to Father one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.64,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:24.94,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't face Mother like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.36,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, Mel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.03,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.00,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.46,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.21,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:55.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to leave the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:07:01.18,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return to the capital \Nand talk to Father—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.77,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:05.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you went back now,\N you'd only get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:09.53,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But if you decide to stay \Nwith us, I'll keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:12.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I can promise you that, if nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.37,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us, Mel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.29,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We leave before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.77,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.54,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we headed, Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I've already got a place in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:45.35,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:47.11,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You knew it had to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:49.52,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We can't cross these mountains on a wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:52.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come back to get it \Nonce this all settles down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:56.03,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You promise to come back for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:56.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:33.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a break here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.03,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.66,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You all right, Second Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.49,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,She must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:49.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama, what made you choose Siltvelt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:51.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The extra security.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:56.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a reason they're trying \Nso hard to prevent us from going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.39,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It might be the perfect place to flee to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:00.01,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:01.64,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:14.01,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.24,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.74,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,What happened between you and Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.37,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:32.16,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,But Mother said to treat \Nthe Shield Hero well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:37.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \NI've heard nothing about your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.47,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,She's the queen of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:44.47,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,That means she's higher than \NFather in the pecking order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The queen's more powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:50.86,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Melromarc is a matrilineal monarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:55.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that king married\N into the royal family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:56.98,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:59.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,He acts like he owns the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.57,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,So what if he married into the family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:03.16,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But he's adopted royalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:07.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:26.15,main,Kni,0000,0000,0000,,They're not over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:28.75,main,Kni,0000,0000,0000,,They can't have gone far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:29.89,main,Kni,0000,0000,0000,,Find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.42,main,Kni,0000,0000,0000,,Look for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.11,main,Kni,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:50.12,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They've blocked this route off, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:51.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's backtrack a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.38,main,Kni,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:06.56,main,Kni,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They found us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:09.97,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Can you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.18,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.23,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're making a break for it\N past that big rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.17,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere left to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:37.79,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,You're are surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:41.68,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Cease your resistance and release \NPrincess Melty at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:45.14,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,"Release"? It's not like I have her tied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:48.60,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Quit lying. We have all the proof we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:52.09,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes, I'm perfectly fine, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:55.93,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,The Shield Hero kept me safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:12:00.81,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on. Didn't Naofumi abduct you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:05.48,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,A dastardly plot was behind all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:09.80,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him to take me and protect my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:11.54,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,"Protect"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:16.50,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,What could the Shield Hero possibly \Nstand to gain by abducting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.31,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,The queen told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:25.46,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,This is the time for all of us to work \Ntogether to thwart the catastrophes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:30.81,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Our world cannot withstand any \Nfurther pointless conflict!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.63,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Please put your weapons away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:37.58,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,As she says, this is a setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:40.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:41.60,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.74,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't listen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:47.49,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,That devil possesses a brainwashing shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:53.22,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,That accursed shield lets him take over \None's mind just by talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... Who would believe such a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:13:00.63,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Heroes Church has found that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:04.47,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,heretics who worship the Shield have \Nstarted popping up in the past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.71,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Heroes Church again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:10.57,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,The Devil of the Shield called himself \N"the Savior of the Heavenly Fowl"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.98,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,and went around brainwashing \Ninnocent people!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.88,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:18.08,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Melty, you poor thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:21.65,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,I see the Devil of the Shield \Nhas already brainwashed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.61,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:26.99,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Then Raphtalia-chan and Filo-chan were \Nreally brainwashed by Naofumi, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.28,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.96,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We've not brainwashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:34.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If my shield had an ability like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:35.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,we wouldn't be in this \Nsituation to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:38.70,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no guarantee that it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:41.45,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any proof to convince us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:47.55,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi, hand over the second princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:51.17,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you she won't \Nbe harmed in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:57.23,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we can avoid fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:13:59.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,that might be for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:04.65,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right, Ren-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:08.32,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Melty's safety comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:16.02,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Come, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.56,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:20.36,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:23.19,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,If I go back, I'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:33.42,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:36.26,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.32,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:48.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ren, I appreciate your offer,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:51.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't trust that woman \Nwith the second princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:54.32,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:15:00.03,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:02.80,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Melty is my dear sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:03.49,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:08.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be crown princess so badly \Nthat you're willing to kill your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:13.75,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You'll say you're undoing the "brainwashing" \Nand kill her when nobody's looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:16.06,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that's what you're planning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I did promise to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:22.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.57,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.34,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:25.09,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,I've called for backup. \NThere's no escape for you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.80,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:33.02,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Filo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.06,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:37.93,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I-I've lost all my strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:43.02,top,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I had the royal alchemists make this \Nso you could stay an angel forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.61,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,As source of thy power, I order thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:51.08,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Decipher the laws of nature and slice \Nthrough my target like a blade of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:52.87,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Zweit Aqua Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:57.83,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I won't miss next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:59.58,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Unhand Filo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.38,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Myne-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:09.62,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill Princess Melty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:12.82,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one who attacked first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:14.68,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Zweit Hellfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.43,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Zweit Fire Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.55,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is wrong with you? Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.80,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't undo her brainwashing, \Nshe'll have to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:29.95,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:33.20,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Can I leave Mel-san to you for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.49,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Step back a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:40.49,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Rage Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:44.50,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Filo-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.51,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,That shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:58.47,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Bring down the hammer of justice \Non the Devil of the Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.68,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.70,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Not on my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:22.46,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,My turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:29.59,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,Annihilate the Devil of the Shield\N and his party!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.01,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.23,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,What's that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:55.32,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:57.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ren...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:03.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I know you'll be able to figure out\Nwhat's really going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.54,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Naofumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.31,sign_7295_24_Soul_Soothing_Po,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(401,1)}Disarming Successful
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.31,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:30.69,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.73,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,She's on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:38.15,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of the Shadows, an espionage \Nsquad under the queen's direct control.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:40.24,main,Shad,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:43.73,main,Shad,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I meet \Nyou in this form, I daresay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:45.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, "daresay"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:50.71,main,Shad,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:55.79,main,Shad,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Hero, you are requested to meet with \NHer Majesty the Queen, I daresay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:57.75,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,With the queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.60,main,Shad,0000,0000,0000,,This commotion has a \Ndeep-rooted cause, I daresay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:03.98,main,Shad,0000,0000,0000,,We would like your help, I daresay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:10.36,main,Shad,0000,0000,0000,,This abduction is a setup by those who \Nfind your accomplishments alarming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:13.14,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, great. More pains in \Nthe ass to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:16.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And? What would I gain by meeting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:21.37,main,Shad,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand once you do, I daresay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:31.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The queen's in the opposite \Ndirection from Siltvelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:34.78,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Second Princess,\N do you know this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:38.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Second Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:40.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,you can use magic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.51,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,...me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.21,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, Second Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.76,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:49.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:55.02,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I have a name! It's Melty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:59.15,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,So why do you keep calling me \N"Second Princess," Shield Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.78,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like some outsider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:06.04,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you call me "Shield Hero," too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:08.72,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like that, \NI'll call you Naofumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:11.79,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,So you call me Melty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:14.90,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Naofumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:16.69,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Straight to first names?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:19.05,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha, Second Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.10,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:20.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Melty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:23.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:25.22,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.64,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:28.98,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Say my name one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:31.04,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Melty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:33.71,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,And don't you forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:36.69,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Also, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:38.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:42.81,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:47.66,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:40.01,sign_81788_789_Walking_Over_Cor,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(356,1)}Everlasting Memory
